  ### Ion Popescu (id 1): are AMBELE coordonate
PUT {{host}}/api/Consilieri/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "numeComplet": "Ion Popescu",
  "email": "ion.popescu@slobozia.ro",
  "telefon": "+40720123456",
  "activ": true
}

### Vasile Georgescu (id 3): doar EMAIL
PUT {{host}}/api/Consilieri/3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "numeComplet": "Vasile Georgescu",
  "email": "vasile.georgescu@slobozia.ro",
  "telefon": null,
  "activ": true
}

### Test Filtru (id 7): FĂRĂ coordonate
PUT {{host}}/api/Consilieri/7
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

{
  "numeComplet": "Test Filtru",
  "email": null,
  "telefon": null,
  "activ": true
}



